The paper discusses a novel technique based on deep learning, which is a common topic in the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), and social and information networks (cs.SI). The paper's focus on classification and prediction also aligns with these sub-categories. Among these, cs.LG is the most likely sub-category as it specifically deals with the study of machine learning algorithms and their applications.
